Welcome to the start of Season Six. A new season, with new wrestlers and amazing non scripted combat. A season that promises everything you have come to love and more.
Madison Young finished last season strong. She is small but amazingly tough and feisty. If you get on the mat with her you're going to be sore the next day win or lose. Madison has her sights on the Championship this year - a goal we think is reachable.
Karrlie Dawn is new to Ultimate Surrender, but she put up an amazing fight. Out classed and out wrestled, she never gave in and never quit. Even when Madison was fingering her, she never stopped fighting, long after most girls would have given in to the pleasure. Karrlie will be back!
title: Madison Young "The Butcher" (0-0)
